Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}五月29日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 你的熱牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要不要試一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽冥 黑客他們賣的咀嚼煙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要來一點點 你就會覺得像上了天堂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫知道我是誰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么時候開始在我的地盤賣這種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這里是交給Bonfa管的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他說 Satoshi Batista先生想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則你丫就該上天堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的挺快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他下藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們過來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北京烤鴨！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人煩躁的遮光蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從車頭到4號車 無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7號車 無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去5、6號車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricardo君 Ricardo君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什么 司機說想出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長 今晚的菜單是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 我可不能空手回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶著名為Michiko Malandro的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Jambo 什么叫感謝我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要下地獄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一個很厲害的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到了Goinia Hiroshi在等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙見到我以后大哭一場 流著鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是痛哭流涕 非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣我們三個人一起過的非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天、每天都笑聲不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你好像不是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經沒有往日的那種棱角了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10號車到13號車無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 仔細看好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我在看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越看越覺得不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說 確實看到這兩個人登上了火車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到她們下車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是商業運輸所以不會載人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是經常檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以出發了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從乘車開始到這里 一路上所有的道路安排檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的道路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上8點 有個人你安排把她送走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的明天付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是護照和身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實交代 說不定我會留你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么來的是黑客？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的手槍正瞄準著你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我扣動扳機...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我的手槍扳機有點松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是給Bonfa打了電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么說是Bonfa那個混蛋出賣了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到我說話了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Monstro現在所有人都是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke那個家伙成了老大 和黑客聯手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想給他個機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Desfiladeiro市發現了Satoshi丟棄的汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Desfiladeiro？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必搞成這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實地說聲對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才像個成年人的作為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}五月30日 Desfiladeiro車站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你辦得到吧 Jazz
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么還不出發 我都要打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 這不是Jambo嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都厭倦了 你只會這一種模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偶爾也該下個決心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 你搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 藥性還沒有消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 我不會去找你的 絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己過來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么是你 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚8點 我為你準備了車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實坐上卡車離開這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子我會照看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會善待她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫說什么傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白我是在幫你逃跑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕再次被Hiroshi弄的傷心流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會傷心流淚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫干什么 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殺掉那個女人之前我要先殺掉你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人留給你什么 你意識到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是大路朝天個走一邊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今怎么可能破鏡重圓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我重說一邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天你丫、你丫的 到底是誰只有一種模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩子當作王牌 就是你做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說的好像你都明白一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你的事情只有我最清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什么人背叛的時候 你立刻就成了廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 Atsuko你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識Michiko Malandro吧 她和你在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 一直向前走就能見到她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 和Hiroshi簡直是一個模子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個男人的什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親不是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人已經上了我的死亡名單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次只要讓我見到 立刻殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再丟點垃圾在尸體上 連神看到都會贊不絕口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 知道Hiroshi在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶路的 所以請答應我不要對Michiko下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么 交易嗎 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的約定我可以答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和說好的不一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳下來 跳下來 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin！ Hatchin！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么！ 為什么要礙我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己我也活到現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會讓那個家伙和自己都幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我的心情怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是礙事的話 我會全力打到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種家伙 要是不和你相識就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？ 這就是我的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會忘記你 忘記所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫的這么親密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面時我們就是陌路人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:22.99,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}追いかけて　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:22.99,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}追赶着 追赶着
